<plot>Simon, a Swedish photographer living in New York's Harlem, answers his doorbell one day to find his grandmother, his MORMOR, standing at his doorstep. Mormor, tired of her sheltered Swedish retirement home, has eloped to join Simon in the freedoms of New York life. Now Simon has to figure out what to do with his eighty-two year old grandmother - and how to explain that naked black man in his bed...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?377513</url></doc>
